Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.01,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.01,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Yutaka Takenouchi and\NI'm the boss of Year 1 at Cro-High.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and I finally came back to Japan\Nafter wandering around in the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:39.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But of all days,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:43.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,why the hell does it have to be on\Nthe day of another school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.04,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe UI\fs26\shad0\be2\pos(171.07,193)}↙{\fs30}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Takenouchi's back at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Guys, don't look behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's got that really scary look on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't there two Takenouchis?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:58.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Damn! And here I was all relieved\Nthat he got switched with a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:01:59.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! You knew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? He was a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:03.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! It's come up to my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:04.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the only thing I can do is erase\N the images of "nauseating" and "throwing up"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,from my head with strength of mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I need resolve! Concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Forget it, forget it, forget it, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay! I've forgotten it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've just completely erased\N the words "throwing up" from my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with transportation, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble! Takenouchi's\Ngoing on a rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Someone, stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Takeshi Hokuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:40.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I participated in a school trip as a step towards\Nreigning over the pig-like masses in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I carelessly got on the wrong train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fnSegoe UI\fs26\shad0\be2\pos(220,150)}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hokuto, I went and bought some tea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Moreover, I'm with this fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just because I took a wild guess\Nand got on this train...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look. If there's something you\Ndon't know, ask people first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's a basic thing any person should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:01.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since no one is going to bother us here, \NI can work in peace on a plan for controlling Cromartie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:08.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,While those idiots are just excited about the trip, we're discussing the conquest of this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's an incredibly pleasant feeling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're talking about pretty pathetic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.75,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,0)\shad0\bord0\c&H0E1014&\fnAnna\pos(313.816,92)}{\frz-10}Maeda, who also{\frz-12} got{\frz-14} on{\frz-16} the wrong{\frz-17} t{\frz-17.2}r{\frz-17.8}a{\frz-18.2}i{\frz-18.8}n.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd go someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on our school trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Normally I'd fudgin' kill them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but if I move carelessly, I'll throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? I came up with a haiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.48,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnSmilecomix\fs28\an8\shad0\bord2\c&H141014&\pos(358,5)\3c&HF0EA88&\be2}On an aimless trip {\alphaff}- Some get wasted by drinking Riding gets me wasted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.85,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnSmilecomix\fs28\an8\shad0\bord2\c&H141014&\pos(358,5)\3c&HF0EA88&\be2}On an aimless trip - Some get wasted by drinking {\alphaff}- Riding gets me wasted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.15,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnSmilecomix\fs28\an8\shad0\bord2\c&H141014&\pos(358,5)\3c&HF0EA88&\be2}On an aimless trip - Some get wasted by drinking - Riding gets me wasted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,On an aimless trip\N Some get wasted by drinking \NRiding gets me wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is bad! I'm getting sicker and sicker, thinking about pointless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&\pos(358,408)}You gotta have non-alcoholic when taking a trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I can't throw up. I have to bear it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:42.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To people who get motion sickness,\Nthe act of throwing up means losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:44.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:48.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Taking care of these fools can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&\pos(430.506,435)}Burp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&\pos(283.228,435)}Blerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.54,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\pos(354.601,120)\fs33\fnArial\shad0\bord0\c&H655056&}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:50.66,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\pos(354.601,120)\fs33\fnArial\shad0\bord0\c&H655056&\clip(m 273 115 l 360.25 115 378.375 110 395.375 110 418 115 456.625 118 452 78 273 85)}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.17,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\pos(354.601,120)\fs33\fnArial\shad0\bord0\c&H655056&}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:52.25,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\pos(354.601,120)\fs33\fnArial\shad0\bord0\c&H655056&\clip(m 267.375 118 l 352.375 121 369.375 108 384 97 403.375 90 268.5 89)}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:52.50,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\pos(354.601,120)\fs33\fnArial\shad0\bord0\c&H655056&\clip(m 267.375 118 l 372.75 123 378.375 113 388.625 102 404.5 91 268.5 89)}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I gotta throw up soon.\NI feel like I'm gonna pass out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That voice is Kamiyama's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I thought I hadn't seen him around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I didn't realize he was\Nsetting a trap like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now you're on my list of people to fudgin' kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So you found me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who are you, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Maeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right, you're Maeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The restroom should be available by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I gotta pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I knew I drank too many\Nnon-alcoholic beverages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you guys doing?!\NGo to the other restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, the other restroom is out of order,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so everyone came to this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but Kamiyama's still in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:27.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm still in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're still in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Phew, I feel refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? What are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm going first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shut up, small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll go first so you all wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?! We were\Nwaiting in line before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:44.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All of you lack calmness right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In that sense, since I feel refreshed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:53.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can judge matters very calmly and neutrally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Won't you please allow me\Nto manage the situation here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:00.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's certainly possible that it would\Nall come out in one burst if I fight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It'd be safer to follow what\NKamiyama says for the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter what we say,\N Takenouchi is the strongest fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If we have to fight one-on-one, it's possible\Nthat it would all come out in one burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll follow what Kamiyama says for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.00,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\q2\an7\pos(5.665,0)\fs20\shad0\fnAnna\fscx101.962\blur0.3\c&H5C6369&\3c&HCFD7DC&\bord2}Kogawa | Badass A | Badass B |Takenouchi |\N Hokuto's lackey | Hokuto | Kamiyama | Maeda |\N Hayashida | Masked Takenouchi | Freddie | Gorilla
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:13.75,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.527\shad0\bord0\c&H584BBE&\blur0.4\move(374.994,481,367.063,420,23,190)}Hit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.00,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.527\shad0\bord0\c&H584BBE&\blur0.4\pos(367.063,420)}Hit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To be fair, we'll draw lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Did everyone write their name in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:21.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs12\fnArial\shad0\bord0\c&H655056&\pos(450.899,190)}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, then, I'll check it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I also don't know which one will hit,\Nso it is completely fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We got it! Do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:29.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why are you going in again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Makiko Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Correction, I'm Noboru Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.61,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,350)}Destrade High School, Year 1 Boss\NNoboru Yamaguchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm heading to Kyoto today
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,because I'm invited to a relative's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course, there's only one goal\Nthat I'd like to achieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:45.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,which is cracking all my relatives up\Nwith my stand-up comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}May I have your attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:50.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}Is there a doctor among the passengers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,1200)\c&HB7D2DC&}If there is, please come to the\Nsecond car immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If this was a comedy skit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:57.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,after this, they'd say "is there a\Nconductor among the passengers?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and then there'd be the snappy\Ncomeback of "that's dangerous!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a conventional TV comedy pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}May I have your attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}Is there a sumo wrestler among the passengers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:11.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}If there is, please come to the\Nsecond car immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a sumo wrestler's version...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But a first-class comedian like myself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be surprised by\Nsomething of this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Rather, I'd point out its faults\Nif it was a comedy script.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}Is there a green grocer among the passengers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A doctor, a sumo wrestler, and a green grocer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the connection among those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:35.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, the second car is\Nin THAT kind of situation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, I see, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no way THAT kind of situation happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.42,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fnSmilecomix\shad0\bord2\be1\3c&H222B39&\pos(556.259,389)}Snappy comeback
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, just because she's an amateur,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean she can say anything she wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Freddie's horse is on the rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.09,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\blur0.5\fad(280,0)\shad0\bord0\fnAnna\frz13.794\pos(655.956,200)\c&H313137&}Sumo\N wrestlers
