Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\blur0.5\shad0\bord0\fnAnna\c&H313137&\frz2.438\pos(189.196,446.5)}Green\N grocer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Aren't there more sumo wrestlers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give him some carrots, so calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good luck, sumo wrestlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm still too normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,things finally regained composure on the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and it has become like a school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But now a big problem has occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}The train will soon arrive in Shin-Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We passed Kyoto long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}Shin-Osaka Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I should never have said such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How long will it be before we get to Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You don't know something as\Nobvious as that? I'm speechless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll take a nap so wake us up\Nwhen we get to Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's my fault because I was sleeping carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, this train has\Ncome all the way to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's still Osaka, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:39.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:43.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? The station we're\Ngonna get off at is Kyoto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can't you even tell the difference\Nbetween Osaka and Kyoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They don't even understand the basics...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These guys are off the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:55.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'd like us to study about Japan today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:55.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:08:05.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\blur0.3\shad0\bord0\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\c&H313137&\pos(175.601,177)}Kyoto
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:08:05.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\blur0.3\shad0\bord0\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\c&H313137&\pos(103.095,201)}Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:08:05.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\blur0.3\shad0\bord0\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\c&H313137&\pos(595.911,262)}Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is Tokyo where everyone lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And there's Osaka ahead of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In other words, Kyoto is\Nbetween Tokyo and Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,using a map made it easy\N to understand and we appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But we're not that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, we haven't gotten to Kyoto yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Uh, yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB7D2DC&}The train will soon arrive in Hakata, the last stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To hell with the explanation at this point!\NThe train will soon arrive in Hakata, the last stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:33.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please listen carefully!\NThis train's not going to Kyoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if we stay on this train longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it is absolutely impossible for us to get to Kyoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What did you say? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We have to change trains, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, Kyoto's far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:49.50,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H54281E&\shad0\bord0\fnAnna\pos(11.329,1)}Hakata
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, Kyoto's far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna switch to an express train next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How can I explain it to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,we are riding on a bullet train again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:57.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I don't know where\Nthis bullet train is heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or I should say, I don't even know\Nif this is a bullet train anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.22,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord12\be20\c&H0E1014&\fnAnna\frx22\fry10\frz-10\3c&HF1F1F1&\move(215.253,78,317.215,78,0,2170)}The Hokuto Corps joined\N the trip at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that there's this incredible thing\Ncalled "The Golden Pavilion" in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The Golden Pavilion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is that like the lottery?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah... probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think the winner gets gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's why it's called "The Golden Pavilion."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:19.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,S-So are you saying that at "The Silver Pavilion"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can get silver coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:27.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And do they let delinquents\N like us play that lottery too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Society really is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:34.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Enough of that conversation.\NIt makes me dizzy just listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we'll be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! We're already arriving?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice, so we'll get off, huh?
