Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We finally got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The school trip was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, this was a train bringing us back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnSmilecomix\shad3\4a&H80\bord1\be1\3c&H222B39&\c&H3CBED8&\pos(138.215,428)}Journey\N of the Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, the trip was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, there wasn't anything\N especially memorable to me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Could it be that we didn't go to Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, let's make it clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We dodge issues when they inconvenience us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why people laugh at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:13.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't blame yourself any longer, Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The act of taking a trip
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,is something that stays only in the\Nhearts of the people who took the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if a person took pictures of the scenery,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:24.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,if it didn't stay in his heart,\Nit's the same as if he didn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please try remembering, carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the memories that stayed in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks. We're the ones who were thoughtless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now we can tell if we went\Non a trip or not with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As we thought, we didn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:41.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we get our deposit back...
