Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\blur0.5\shad0\bord0\fnAnna\pos(531.335,72)\c&H315547&}Mr. Masao working
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For this anime, I want it to be put\Nnot only in anime section,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but also in artist section.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Takenouchi too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I love transportation!
